docs {
  ## Review Store Requisition
  ส่งใบเบิกสินค้ากลับไปยังขั้นตอนก่อนหน้าเพื่อแก้ไข

  Returns a store requisition to a previous workflow stage for corrections. Allows approvers to request changes before granting final authorization.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `id` | string (UUID) | Store Requisition ID |

  ### Query Parameters
  | Name | Type | Required | Default | Description |
  |------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
  | `version` | string | No | latest | API version |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `inventory_management.store_requisition:view` (with approval role)
  - **Roles**: HOD, Approval

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "stage_role": "create",
    "des_stage": "HOD",
    "details": []
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "sr_no": "SR-2026-0001"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | SR is not in a state that can be reviewed |
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User is not authorized to review at this stage |
  | 404 | Store Requisition or target stage not found |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}

params:path {
  id: {{sr_id}}
}
